node.text:
A shade so provocative deserves its own holiday. Happy #NationalOrgasmDay. 

What started in 1999 as the explosively fresh peachy-pink shade has evolved into a global icon, maintaining its cult-classic status for over 20 years. The bestselling shade has since inspired an entire collection of formulas and textures, designed to treat every temptation. Shop all the sensations of Orgasm at narscosmetics.com.
